Ghanaian Pastor, Mensa Otabil will be joining Bishop Mike Okonkwo, Rev. Yinka Yusuf and Senior Pastor, Trinity House, Ituah Ighodalo to minister at the second annual word and power conference of Trinity House. According to a statement made available to THISDAY yesterday by the convener, Pastor Ituah Ighodalo, it was noted that the conference which would begin from April 3-7 has as the theme: ‘Set Time’ would take place at the church main auditorium, Zion Centre, situated on Trinity Avenue, through Water Corporation Road, off Ligali Ayorinde Street, Victoria Island, Lagos. The conference will take place from 5p.m weekdays (Wednesday to Friday) and end with a celebration service at 9a.m on Sunday.